## 🎨 1000x PREMIUM UX/UI STANDARDS

We are completely abandoning "boring spreadsheet" design. The new CRM will look and feel like a high-end, luxury command center.

- **Data Representation:** NO tables. All data (Students, Clients, Staff) will be displayed as beautiful, interactive **Card Grids** with profile images, status badges, and quick-action menus.
- **Workflow:** ALL pipelines and project management will use visual, drag-and-drop **Kanban Boards**.
- **"Invisible UI":** Contextual slide-out sheets for editing, eliminating heavy page loads.
- **Theme Logic:** Seamless Auto-detect System Preference (Dark/Light) using Gold-tinted premium Glassmorphism.

---

## 🗄️ GLOBAL DATABASE & API ARCHITECTURE (FUTURE-PROOFED)

### 1. The Client Portal API (Built for Day 1)
- The Supabase database will be structured with a secure API layer specifically designed for **B2B/B2C Clients**.
- In the future (1-2 months), clients will log into custom Android/iOS apps (or a web portal) to track their Software Project milestones or Study Abroad Visa status in real-time.

### 2. Global Communication Hub (Real-time)
- **Database Tables:** `chat_rooms`, `chat_messages`, `team_groups`.
- **Features:** Direct messaging, Group chats (National/International teams), and Global Company Announcements.
- **Future:** Voice/Video calling system integrated for cross-office collaboration.

### 3. Nexus Digital "All-In-One" Engine
- **Sales/Leads Pipeline:** Tracking enterprise clients from discovery to won contracts.
- **Project Management (Dev/Delivery):** Once won, the client moves to the PM module.
  - Tracking Sprints, Dev Timelines, Milestones, Client Approvals, and AI Automation deliverables.

### 4. Staff Tagging & Super Admin Control
- Strict role-based row-level security (RLS).
- Unified dashboards for staff working across multiple companies.
- Only Super Admins can assign website CMS access or manage global permissions.

