## 🌐 CRM NAVIGATION (THE NEW COMMAND CENTER)

### Executive Command (Super Admin Only)
- **Global Dashboard:** Visual analytics, combined global revenue, separate company performance metrics, and top-level KPIs.

### Communications & Workflow
- **Unified Task Center:** Kanban board of all tasks assigned to the user across the entire holding company.
- **Global Comms Hub:** Internal chat, team groups, and global announcements.
- **Global Consultations:** Shared cross-company calendar.

### GT Group Nexus Digital (End-to-End)
- **Enterprise Leads:** B2B/B2C Sales Pipeline (Kanban).
- **Project Command:** Software/AI Development Milestones, Client Approvals.
- **Website CMS:** Nexus Services, Portfolio, Case Studies.

### GT Group Study Abroad
- **Prospective Students:** Admissions Pipeline (Kanban).
- **Website CMS:** Universities, Destinations, Scholarships, Programs.

### Global Operations (Core)
- **Corporate Address Book:** Visual Card Grid of B2B partners.
- **Office Schedule & HR:** Team availability and attendance.
- **Financial Control:** Revenue, Budgeting, and Reimbursements.
- **Global Assets & Inventory:** Equipment tracking.
- **Super Admin Settings:** CCTV, API Keys, Permissions.

